      <hedline>
        <hl1>Absolutely, Power Corrupts</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>I remember the old Brooklyn Dodgers when players like Pee Wee Reese and Jackie Robinson woudl do whatever they had to to get on base. They would bunt or even get hit with a pitch just to get on base. They would get the opposing pitchers crazy and then steal a base. That was baseball.</p>
        <p>Martin Blumberg  Woodbury, N.Y.</p>
      </block>
